🔤 TYPOGRAPHY
Primary font: Inter (Google Fonts)

URL: https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700
Weights used: 400 (body), 500 (labels, buttons, nav), 600 (headings, page titles), 700 (bold)
Letter spacing: -0.01em on headings, -0.02em on large display titles, +0.04em on ALL-CAPS labels
Monospace font: JetBrains Mono (Google Fonts)

URL: https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500
Used for: batch numbers, MICR fields, amounts, cheque numbers, employee IDs
